org.miktim.websocket

Class WsStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miktim.websocket.WsStatus

  • public final class WsStatus
extends Object
    WebSocket status.

    The class contains public properties and WebSocket predefined close codes.
    - RFC6455 section-7.4;
    - IANA close codes;
    - MDN CloseEvent codes.
